This is step by step to ensure all running successfully:
1. Open terminal and make sure that you cd into the project directory and then run this command in terminal:
 
 python -m venv venv

2. Activate the virtual environment (Windows) by using this command:

.\venv\Scripts\activate

3. Then run this command to install all requirements:

pip install -r requirements.txt

4. Then, you need to download ollama to run LLM Model locally at https://ollama.com/

5. After you're done downloading it, install it in your system.

6. Then open Command Prompt (CMD), then run this command:

ollama pull llama3

7. After it finishes, run this command to run llamma3:

ollama run llama3

8. After thats done, you now have llama3 run on your local machine.

9. After thats done, you can go back to the folder before then run this command:

streamlit run app.py
